        "derivation": "\\theta = \\frac{360^\\circ}{60} \\times 5 = 30^\\circ \\Rightarrow \\text{Area} = \\frac{30^\\circ}{360^\\circ} \\times \\frac{22}{7} \\times 14^2 \\Rightarrow \\text{Area} = \\frac{1}{12} \\times \\frac{22}{7} \\times 196 = \\frac{1}{12} \\times 22 \\times 28 = \\frac{616}{12} = \\frac{154}{3} \\text{ cm}^2"
